ggplot(data = MOJO, aes(x = year, y = EN.ATM.CO2E.PC, color = country)) + 
  geom_point(alpha = 0.8) + 
  theme_bw() + 
  guides(color = FALSE) + 
  labs(y = "CO2 emissions (metric tons per capita)")

MOJOusa <- subset(MOJO, country == "North America")
ggplot(data = MOJOusa, aes(x = year, y = EN.ATM.CO2E.PC)) + 
  geom_point(alpha = 0.8) + 
  theme_bw() + 
  guides(color = FALSE) + 
  labs(y = "CO2 emissions (metric tons per capita)")

HRP <- WDI(country = "all", indicator = c("SP.POP.TOTL", "NY.GDP.MKTP.CD", "SP.DYN.LE00.IN", "NY.GDP.PCAP.PP.CD", "SP.DYN.TFRT.IN", "SI.POV.2DAY"),
    start = 1960, end = 2015, extra = FALSE, cache = NULL)
HRP <- HRP %>%
  rename(Population = SP.POP.TOTL, GDPinUS = NY.GDP.MKTP.CD, LifeExpectancy = SP.DYN.LE00.IN, GDPpci = NY.GDP.PCAP.PP.CD, FertilityRate = SP.DYN.TFRT.IN, Poverty = SI.POV.2DAY)
